---
title: Savoury Braised Chickpeas & Shrimp with Feta and Lemon-Garlic Toum
description: Protein-packed chickpeas get a flavour boost from warm Indian-style spices in this hearty and fragrant stew. You'll want to scoop up every last bit of this veggie-filled wonder!
